item.title: Empire Core
item.description: Agent Types Within Empire, the implant currently uses two primary languages: Python - any platform that supports python 2.5+ PowerShell - any Windows platform that supports PowerShell v2 Its not always clear what and where something works when you begin to support multi-platform architecture such as Empire. This has always been a design challenge for the development team to keep it clean and logical. Empire as a project has multiple supported platforms, but simply we have built for the core three operating systems:
